		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2005/05/any-idea-how-hard-it-is-to-find-the-internet-in-moscow/" rel="bookmark">Any idea how hard it is to find the internet in Moscow?</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Hard. Really hard.<br />
Amy and I got here yesterday morning, but you&#8217;d be surprised how hard it is to find an internet cafe. Our hotel, Rossiya, despite being the largest hotel in Europe (which, incidentally, isn&#8217;t remotely as cool as it sounds), doesn&#8217;t have jack sqwat.<br />
