<article id="post-524" class="post-524 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-travel tag-around-the-world tag-russia tag-soviet-union tag-st-petersburg">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2005/05/16-years-ago/" rel="bookmark">16 years ago&#8230;</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p><cite>[This entry originally posted on <a href="http://www.howtogetlost.com/">How To Get Lost</a>: <a href="http://www.howtogetlost.com/2005/05/04/16-years-ago/">16 years ago&#8230;</a>.]</cite><br />
I had a phone chat with Alex this morning (it hasn&#8217;t been a week, and I miss her sorely; the next six weeks almost seem unfathomable), and she let me know something.<br />
I&#8217;ve gotten a little carried away saying &#8220;16 years ago&#8221;.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2005/05/16-years-ago/#more-524" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;16 years ago&#8230;&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2005/05/16-years-ago/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2005-05-04T01:54:35-06:00">4 May 2005</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/travel/" rel="category tag">Travel</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/around-the-world/" rel="tag">around the world</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/russia/" rel="tag">russia</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/soviet-union/" rel="tag">soviet union</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/st-petersburg/" rel="tag">st. petersburg</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2005/05/16-years-ago/#respond">Leave a comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on 16 years ago&#8230;</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
